            <entry xml:id="entry_gærz" xml:lang="os">
                <form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>gærz</orth></form>
                <form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>gærzæ</orth></form>
                <sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                        <q>ремень</q>
                    </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                        <q>strap</q>
                    </abv:tr></sense>
                <re>
                    <form type="lemma"><orth>gærz ron</orth></form>
                    <sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>ременной пояс</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>belt</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense>
                </re>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Ср. <mentioned xml:lang="sva"><lang/>
                        <w>gärs</w>
                        <gloss><q>кожица</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/>
                        <w>garsi</w>
                        <gloss><q>кожица</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>скорлупа</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><lang/>
                        <w>kars</w>
                        <gloss><q>аркан</q></gloss></mentioned>. Не исключено иранское
                    происхождение; ср. <mentioned xml:lang="zkh"><lang/>
                        <w>кšyк</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru"> (из *%iкaršiк%i? <bibl><ref
                                    type="bibl" target="#ref_Henning._Khwar."
                                    /><biblScope>12</biblScope></bibl>)</note><note type="comment"
                            xml:lang="en"> (from *%iкaršiк%i? <bibl><ref type="bibl"
                                    target="#ref_Henning._Khwar."
                            /><biblScope>12</biblScope></bibl>)</note>
                        <gloss><q>ремень</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">Compare <mentioned xml:lang="sva"><lang/>
                        <w>gärs</w>
                        <gloss><q>thin skin</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/>
                        <w>garsi</w>
                        <gloss><q>thin skin</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>shell</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><lang/>
                        <w>kars</w>
                        <gloss><q>lasso</q></gloss></mentioned>. Iranian origin is not excluded;
                    compare <mentioned xml:lang="zkh"><lang/>
                        <w>кšyк</w><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru"> (из *%iкaršiк%i? <bibl><ref
                                    type="bibl" target="#ref_Henning._Khwar."
                                    /><biblScope>12</biblScope></bibl>)</note><note type="comment"
                            xml:lang="en"> (from *%iкaršiк%i? <bibl><ref type="bibl"
                                    target="#ref_Henning._Khwar."
                            /><biblScope>12</biblScope></bibl>)</note>
                        <gloss><q>strap</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym>
            </entry>
